#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/introduction.rst:12
msgid ""
"Holding :kbd:`Ctrl` during a transform operation (such as grab, rotate or "
"scale) will toggle :ref:`Transform Snapping <transform-snap>`. When the :ref:"
"`Snap Element <transform-snap-element>` is set to *Increment*, this allows "
"the transformation to be performed in discrete amounts."
msgstr "Le maintien de :kbd:`Ctrl` "

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/introduction.rst:17
msgid ""
"Holding :kbd:`Shift` during a transform operation will transform the object "
"at 1/10th the speed, allowing much finer control."
msgstr ""
"Le maintien de :kbd:`Maj` pendant une opération de transformation va "
"transformer l'objet au 1/10e de la vitesse, permettant un contrôle beaucoup "
"plus fin."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/introduction.rst:20
msgid ""
"The magnitude of the transformation can be viewed in the 3D View footer. "
"Releasing :kbd:`Ctrl` or :kbd:`Shift` during the transformation will cause "
"the movement to revert back to its normal mode of operation."
msgstr ""
"L'importance de la transformation peut être visualisée en bas de page de la "
"Vue 3D. Relâcher :kbd:`Ctrl` ou :kbd:`Maj` pendant la transformation va "
"faire que le mouvement revient à son mode normal d'opération."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/introduction.rst:24
msgid ""
"Holding both :kbd:`Shift-Ctrl` enables precise snap. This option will move "
"the object with high precision along with the snapping constraint."
msgstr "Le maintien de "

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/introduction.rst:29
msgid ""
"The snapping behaviors described on this page **only** apply when :ref:"
"`Increment Snap <transform-snap-element>` is selected."
msgstr ""
"Les comportements de clipsage décrits dans cette page s'appliquent "
"*uniquement* quand :ref:`Increment Snap <transform-snap-element>` est "
"sélectionné."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/introduction.rst:34
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Utilisation"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/introduction.rst:37
msgid "With Hotkeys"
msgstr "Avec des raccourcis"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/introduction.rst:39
msgid ""
"Press :kbd:`G`, :kbd:`R` or :kbd:`S` and then hold either :kbd:`Ctrl`, :kbd:"
"`Shift` or :kbd:`Shift-Ctrl`."
msgstr ""
"Pressez :kbd:`G`, :kbd:`R` ou :kbd:`S` et ensuite maintenez soit :kbd:"
"`Ctrl`, :kbd:Maj` soit kbd:`Maj-Ctrl`."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/introduction.rst:44
msgid "With the Transform Manipulator"
msgstr "Avec le manipulateur Transform"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/introduction.rst:46
msgid ""
"Hold :kbd:`Ctrl`, :kbd:`Shift` or :kbd:`Shift-Ctrl` and click on the "
"appropriate manipulator handle. Then move the mouse in the desired "
"direction. The reverse action will also work i.e. clicking the manipulator "
"handle and then holding the shortcut key for precision control."
msgstr ""
"Maintenir :kbd:`Ctrl`, :kbd:`Maj` or :kbd:`Maj-Ctrl` et cliquer sur la "
"poignée du manipulateur approprié. Puis déplacez la souris dans la direction "
"souhaitée. L'action inverse va aussi fonctionner à savoir en cliquant sur la "
"poignée du manipulateur et ensuite en maintenant la clé de raccourci pour un "
"contrôle de précision."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/introduction.rst:52
msgid ""
":doc:`Read more about the Transform Manipulator </editors/3dview/object/"
"editing/transform/control/manipulators>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Plus sur le Manipulateur Transform </editors/3dview/object/editing/"
"transform/control/manipulators>`."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/introduction.rst:54
msgid "Combining with Other Controls"
msgstr "Combinaison avec d'autres COntrôles"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/introduction.rst:56
msgid ""
"All of the precision controls detailed on the page can be combined with the :"
"doc:`Axis Locking </editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/"
"precision/axis_locking>` controls and used with the different :doc:`Pivot "
"Points </editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/index>`."
msgstr ""
"Tous les contrôles de précision détaillés sur cette page peuvent être "
"combinés avec les contrôles de :doc:`verrouillage d'axe </editors/3dview/"
"object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking>` et utilisés avec "
"les différents :doc:`Points Pivot </editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/"
"control/pivot_point/index>`."

